title: My 6 Books - November 2014 (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 6 books, 3 PDFs & 3 ePUBs:

1. American Heroes: On the Homefront by Oliver North (Nov 5, 2013)
   
2. Human Geography: A Concise Introduction by Mark Boyle (Nov 24, 2014)
   
3. Principles of Corporate Finance by Richard Brealey and Stewart Myers (Jan 15, 2013)
   
4. The Art of Landscape Photography by Ross Hoddinott (Jun 1, 2015)
   
5. The Night Sky, Updated and Expanded Edition: Soul and Cosmos: The Physics and Metaphysics of the Stars and Planets by Richard Grossinger and Bernadette Mayer (Sep 30, 2014)
   
6. The Old Farmer's Almanac 2015 by Old Farmer's Almanac (Aug 26, 2014)
